# lobo
A simple cli for listing AWS load balancers and their instances/targets.

# Install
```bash
pip install lobo
```

# Usage
```bash
# List all load balancers
$ lobo

# List load balancers which match <name>
$ lobo <name>

# Pass `-s` and/or `-t` to list scheme/type.
```

